# Sales Manager - Ginesys ERP & POS

A comprehensive sales management & activity tracking system for Ginesys sales teams.

## 🎯 Features

- **Sales Rep Dashboard** - Track daily activities, deals, and tasks
- **Manager Dashboard** - Team overview, performance metrics, pipeline
- **Daily Activity Reports (DAR)** - Comprehensive daily reporting
- **Deal Pipeline Management** - Track leads through sales stages
- **Task Management** - Assign and track team tasks
- **Team Leaderboard** - Performance comparison and motivation
- **Activity Logging** - Calls, demos, meetings (all types)
- **No Backend Required** - All data stored locally in browser

